0e2ng\u0103]] {{goal|70}}|\ngoals2= [[Darcy Dolce Neto|Neto]] {{goal|90+4}}|\nstadium= [[Skoda Xanthi Arena]], [[Xanthi]]|\nreferee= G. Daloukas ([[Thessaly]])}}\n----\n{{footballbox|\ndate= 10\u201311 February 2010|\ntime= 17:00|\nteam1= [[Kavala F.C.|Kavala]]|\nscore= 0 \u2013 0|\nteam2= [[Panionios F.C.|Panionios]]|\ngoals1= |\ngoals2= |\nstadium= [[Kavala Stadium]], [[Kavala]]|\nreferee= M. Dakos ([[Xanthi Prefecture|Xanthi]])}}\n\n<small>The match had been interrupted in the 69th minute due to bad condition of grass, that came from continuous raining. According to regulation, the match was continued from minute that had been stopped, 24 hours later (11 February 2010).</small>\n\n===Replays===\n\n{{footballbox|\ndate= 17 February 2010|\ntime= 17:00|\nteam1= [[Aris Thessaloniki F.C.|Aris]]|\nscore= 3 \u2013 0|\nteam2= [[Skoda Xanthi F.C.|Skoda Xanthi]]|\ngoals1= [[Javier C\u00e1mpora|C\u00e1mpora]] {{goal|17}}<br>[[Freddy Adu|Adu]] {{goal|22}}<br>[[Koke (footballer)|Koke]] {{goal|65}}|\ngoals2= |\nstadium= [[Kleanthis Vikelidis Stadium]], [[Thessaloniki]]|\nreferee= G. Stathopoulos ([[Achaea]])}}\n----\n{{footballbox|\ndate= 17 February 2010|\ntime= 17:00|\nteam1= [[Panionios F.C.|Panionios]]|\nscore= 1 \u2013 2 <br> <small>([[Extra time|aet]])</small>|\nteam2= [[Kavala F.C.|Kavala]]|\ngoals1= [[Sito Riera|Riera]] {{goal|47}}|\ngoals2= [[Sini\u0161a Dobrasinovi\u0107|Dobrasinovi\u0107]] {{goal|84}}<br>[[Benjamin Onwuachi|Onwuachi]] {{goal|97}}|\nstadium= [[Nea Smyrni Stadium]], [[Nea Smyrni]] (Athens)|\nreferee= V. Pamporidis ([[Kilkis Prefecture|Kilkis]])}}\n\n==Semi-Finals==\n\n=== 1st leg===\n\n{{footballbox|\ndate= 17 March 2010|\ntime= 17:00|\nteam1= [[Aris Thessaloniki F.C.|Aris]]|\nscore= 3 \u2013 1|\nteam2= [[Kavala F.C.|Kavala]]|\ngoals1= [[Koke (footballer)|Koke]] {{goal|26|pen.}}, {{goal|68}}<br>[[Francisco Javier Peral|Javito]] {{goal|84}}|\ngoals2= [[Benjamin Onwuachi|Onwuachi]] {{goal|45}}|\nstadium= [[Kleanthis Vikelidis Stadium]], [[Thessaloniki]]|\nreferee= A. Kakos ([[Corfu Prefecture|Corfu]])}}\n----\n{{footballbox|\ndate= 24 March 2010|\ntime= 17:00|\nteam1= [[Panathinaikos FC|Panathinaikos]]|\nscore= 3 \u2013 1|\nteam2= [[PAS Giannina F.C.|PAS Giannina]]|\ngoals1= [[Ilias Kotsios|Kotsios]] {{goal|14|o.g.}}<br>[[Sotiris Ninis|Ninis]] {{goal|45}}<br>[[Djibril Ciss\u00e9|Ciss\u00e9]] {{goal|85}}|\ngoals2= [[Georgios Kousas|Kousas]] {{goal|90}}|\nstadium= [[Olympic Stadium (Athens)|Athens Olympic Stadium \"Spyridon Louis\"]], [[Athens]]|\nattendance= 6,695|\nreferee= G. Stathopoulos ([[Achaea]])}}\n\n===2nd leg===\n\n{{footballbox|\ndate= 25 March 2010|\ntime= 17:00|\nteam1= [[Kavala F.C.|Kavala]]|\nscore= 1 \u2013 1 <br> ([[Playoff format#Total points series (aggregate)|agg.]] 2 \u2013 4)|\nteam2= [[Aris Thessaloniki F.C.|Aris]]|\ngoals1= [[Serge Di\u00e9|Di\u00e9]] {{goal|55}}|\ngoals2= [[Koke (footballer)|Koke]] {{goal|44}}|\nstadium= [[Kavala Stadium]], [[Kavala]]|\nreferee= G. Daloukas ([[Thessaly]])}}\n----\n{{footballbox|\ndate= 7 April 2010|\ntime= 17:00|\nteam1= [[PAS Giannina F.C.|PAS Giannina]]|\nscore= 0 \u2013 0 <br> ([[Playoff format#Total points series (aggregate)|agg.]] 1 \u2013 3)|\nteam2= [[Panathinaikos FC|Panathinaikos]]|\ngoals1= |\ngoals2= |\nstadium= [[Zosimades Stadium]], [[Ioannina]]|\nattendance= 5,566|\nreferee= S. Tritsonis ([[Athens]])}}\n\n==Final==\n\nThe 66th Greek Cup Final was played at [[Olympic Stadium (Athens)|Athens Olympic Stadium \"Spyridon Louis\"]] on Saturday, April 24, 2010.\n\nThe last time that the two clubs were met in the Final was in [[Greek Cup 1939-40|1940]] \u2013 Panathinaikos won 3\u20131.\n\nThe last time that Panathinaikos won the Cup was in [[Greek Cup 2003-04|2004]] (3\u20131 against [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]]). The last time that played in a Final was in [[Greek Cup 2006-07|2007]] \u2013 they lost to [[Larissa F.C.|Larissa]] 2\u20131.\n\nThe last time that Aris won the Cup was in [[Greek Cup 1969-70|1970]] (1\u20130 against [[PAOK F.C.|PAOK]]). The last time that played in a Final was in [[Greek Cup 2007-08|2008]] \u2013 they lost to [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] 2\u20130.\n\n{{footballbox\n|date= 24 April 2010\n|time= 20:30\n|team1= [[Panathinaikos FC|Panathinaikos]] [[File:Verde con trifoglio Verde su cerchio Bianco.png|25px]]\n|score=1 \u2013 0\n|report= [http://www.uefa.com/memberassociations/association=gre/news/newsid=1480868.html Report]\n|team2= [[File:Giallo e Nero Aris.JPG|25px]] [[Aris Thessaloniki F.C.|Aris]]\n|goals1= [[Sebasti\u00e1n Leto|Leto]] {{goal|63}}|\n|goals2=\n|stadium= [[Olympic Stadium (Athens)|Athens Olympic Stadium \"Spyridon Louis\"]]\n|attendance= 48,926\n|referee= A. Kakos ([[Corfu Prefecture|Corfu]])\n}}\n\n{| width=92% |\n|-\n|{{Football kit\n|pattern_la= _panathinaikosfc0910h\n|pattern_b = _panathinaikosfc0910h\n|pattern_ra= _panathinaikosfc0910h\n|pattern_sh= _adidaswhite\n|pattern_so= _3_stripes_white\n|leftarm  = 00874B\n|body    = 00874B\n|rightarm  = 00874B\n|shorts    = 00874B\n|socks     = 00874B\n | title      = Panathinaikos\n}}\n|{{Football kit\n| pattern_b  =_arisfc0910\n| pattern_ra =\n| pattern_sh =_black_thinstripe_color\n| pattern_so =_arisfc0810\n| leftarm    =FFFF00\n| body       =FFFF00\n| rightarm   =FFFF00\n| shorts     =FFDF00\n| socks      =FFDF00\n | title      = Aris\n}}\n|}\n\n{| width=\"100%\"\n|valign=\"top\" width=\"50%\"|\n{| style=\"font-size: 90%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"\n|colspan=\"4\"|'''PANATHINAIKOS:'''\n|-\n!width=\"25\"| !!width=\"25\"|\n|-\n|GK ||'''30''' ||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Alexandros Tzorvas]]\n|-\n|DF ||'''24''' ||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Loukas Vintra]]\n|-\n|DF ||'''31''' ||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Nikos Spiropoulos]] || {{yel|30}}\n|-\n|DF ||'''&nbsp;8''' ||{{flagicon|MLI}} [[C\u00e9dric Kant\u00e9]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''29''' ||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Kostas Katsouranis]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''15''' ||{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Gilberto Silva]] [[captain (association football)|(c)]]\n|-\n|MF ||'''&nbsp;7''' ||{{flagicon|GRE}} [[Sotiris Ninis]] || || {{su